data.description: $10K Price drop, home is under market value  book your showing now!  See V-Tour and check out this fabulous home. 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage:    Shows like a new model home and is almost 3,000 Sq ft with the recently installed 403 Sqft lifestyle rear room with a transferable warranty, and lots of natural sun shining on the tile throughout the home and with a new Coffee station next to the fireplace. Master suite has large tub - shower in this royal like bath. The 4th bedroom could also be used as an office or luxury closet. The Sugar Mills County Club   for a small fee offer just so much like Multiple golf courses, swimming, tennis and pickellball at the clubhouse, see their website for all the fun!  Only 45 Min to Tampa International Airport on a limited access road nearby.  kitchen is spacious with Lots of granite countertop space and centrally located . Air Cond 2017 and a new roof in 2010 which is in perfect condition.   See the pictures but better yet view the Interior tour for this fine home !
